# VAYO Karma Points System — Implementation

## Phase 1: Database Layer
- [ ] Create `karma_migration.sql` — karma_ledger table, action_type ENUM, trigger for denormalized `karma_score` on `users`, indexes
- [ ] Add `karma_score` column to `users` table via ALTER

## Phase 2: Pydantic Models
- [ ] Create `karma_models.py` — enums (KarmaActionType, KarmaTier), request/response schemas (KarmaAwardRequest, KarmaLedgerEntry, KarmaProfileResponse, InboxShieldUpdate)

## Phase 3: Karma Service Layer
- [ ] Create `karma.py` — APIRouter with endpoints:
  - `POST /api/v1/karma/award` — append ledger row, return updated score
  - `GET /api/v1/users/{user_id}/karma` — return score + tier + ledger history
  - `PATCH /api/v1/users/{user_id}/inbox-shield` — update inbox shield threshold
  - `GET /api/v1/users/{user_id}/karma/can-message/{target_user_id}` — outbound DM check
  - `GET /api/v1/users/{user_id}/karma/can-join-event/{event_id}` — event eligibility (stub)

